<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida9d0f382-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2781"><num value="2781">§ 2781.</num><heading> Availability of appropriations: exchange fees; losses in accounts</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Amounts appropriated to the Department of Defense may be used for—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="ida9d0f383-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2781/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> exchange fees; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="ida9d0f384-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2781/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> losses in the accounts of disbursing officials and agents in accordance with law.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="ida9d0f385-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/100/370/s1/m/1">Pub. L. 100–370, § 1(m)(1)</ref>, <date date="1988-07-19">July 19, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/849">102 Stat. 849</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
